Leslie David Baker https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Leslie_David_Baker 0 Leslie David Baker (born February 19, 1958) is an American television and film actor. He is known for playing paper salesman Stanley Hudson in The Office for nine seasons. Leslie_David_Baker ( born February_19_,_1958 ) is an_American_television_and_film_actor .
